reviewText:
OMG I just watched this amazing film and the range emotion in the actors was so awe inspiring! This film literally brought tears to my eyes! From the highs to the lows I was with them every step of the way!  The intro was so  ominous! Parrot Dise All the Way!! You guys rock! Is there going to be a sequel?? Ohh and the editing is awesome!

Tim S.
